{"tid":264863,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"利物浦首簽誕生","createTime":"2017-05-31T07:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T08:44:04.000Z","uid":119729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb6cdb23dc516e251c86a34bdff1b8c1724683ee","tid":264863,"uid":119729,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:44:41.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=e9O9amzqvGH8pRtNz3tTuhOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=984614f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英超勁旅利物浦官方宣佈落實購入車路士青訓前鋒蘇蘭基，7月1日動筆簽字，成為球隊今夏首筆收購。<br />\n<br />\n利物浦落實簽下19歲車路士前鋒蘇蘭基（Dominic Solanke），將支付300萬鎊培養費，領隊高普摩拳擦掌，看來會在轉會市場有一番作為。<br />\n<br />\n早在2014年10月，蘇蘭基已為一隊上陣，2015/16年球季借到荷甲的維迪斯，上陣25場，射入7球。<br />\n<br />\n蘇蘭基是英格蘭小國腳，目前代表U20出戰世青盃，披甲3場射入1球，表現不俗。除此之外，此子兩次拿到青年足總盃，一次青年歐聯及U17歐國盃冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/31/154340_391094cd385c35848fcf1b50314a617d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F31%2F154340_391094cd385c35848fcf1b50314a617d.jpg&h=fb58ef11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>此子兩次拿到青年足總盃，一次青年歐聯及U17歐國盃冠軍。</strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span><br />\n<br />\n係未拎過青年英超 襯到絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662d646c4a98a7ef69d0fb67d453590e583b528d","tid":264863,"uid":54025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"佢有d料，真心唔差"},{"pid":"96355cfe726f709e72be267096d3edf179e9d07e","tid":264863,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T07:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f0ff7e721785cd6ad927f317e1d86d42fc6fb8","tid":26